## Fizz Buzz

::: columns
::: {.column width="75%"}

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="false"}
num <- 1:100

for(i in 1:length(num)){
  # Numbers divisible by both 3 and 5
  if(num[i] %% 3 == 0 & num[i] %% 5 == 0){
    print("FizzBuzz")
    } 
  # Numbers divisible by 5
  else if(num[i] %% 5 == 0){
    print("Buzz")
    }
  # Numbers divisible by 3
  else if(num[i] %% 3 == 0){
    print("Fizz")
    } 
  # Numbers not divisible by 3 or 5
  else{
    print(num[i])
    }
  }
```
