## How would I...

use a `while()`-loop to figure out the first dog that needed wet food?

. . .

</br>

::: columns
::: {.column width="48%"}
**Initialize Values**

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="false"}
age <- ""
counter <- 0
```
:::


::: {.fragment}
**Create the Loop**

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code  code-line-numbers="false"}
while(age < 12){
  counter <- counter + 1
  age <- dogs$age[counter]  
}
```
